00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
(Sahaja Yogi talks in German)

00:49:42.999 --> 00:49:45.918
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:49:51.083 --> 00:49:58.417
It is important for all of us to know that we do not know absolute truth.

00:50:05.209 --> 00:50:11.999
One person says something, another person says something, and we don't know where to look.

00:50:19.334 --> 00:50:22.918
We don't know whom to believe and whom to understand.

00:50:28.918 --> 00:50:33.375
Also, whatever I'm telling you, you need not take Me for granted.

00:50:40.292 --> 00:50:44.083
But keep your minds open, as scientists.

00:50:50.000 --> 00:50:57.918
In case what I say is proved, then you have to accept it as law, not because I say this is so, this is so.

00:51:11.250 --> 00:51:19.250
Now, you have heard about the chakras that are within us and the centers that govern us.

00:51:26.042 --> 00:51:29.792
Now, this knowledge is the knowledge of the roots.

00:51:34.417 --> 00:51:38.292
This instrument has come out of the knowledge of the tree.

00:51:45.959 --> 00:51:50.667
But there is another instrument within us about which you have already heard.

00:51:55.959 --> 00:52:04.250
Then one may ask: If there is such an instrument within us, why do we commit mistakes, why do we have collective mistakes also?

00:52:11.959 --> 00:52:17.375
And why it is that we all do not have understand absolute truth?

00:52:22.292 --> 00:52:26.584
And why there are so many different ideas and theories in this world?

00:52:31.209 --> 00:52:34.501
And why do we have this instrument within all of us?

00:52:40.626 --> 00:52:46.167
But this instrument, which is within us, is not connected to the mains.

00:52:51.999 --> 00:52:54.125
That's why it is not working out.

00:52:56.999 --> 00:52:59.292
It has to be connected to the mains.

00:53:02.834 --> 00:53:12.626
And to connect it to the mains is possible today, may not have been few years back.

00:53:21.334 --> 00:53:25.083
So we have to get this instrument working all right.

00:53:31.000 --> 00:53:50.125
As you can see on both the sides, we have left and right side of energy flowing, which gives rise to imbalances within ourselves.

00:53:56.501 --> 00:54:03.667
These two energies of left and right side give rise to two sympathetic nervous systems: of left side and right side.

00:54:12.709 --> 00:54:19.792
But the central energy, which is looking after our balance, is the parasympathetic nervous system.

00:54:27.918 --> 00:54:35.667
For example, if you run fast, you can increase… you… you can increase the beat of you heart.

00:54:42.751 --> 00:54:46.417
But you cannot reduce and bring it to normal.

00:54:51.250 --> 00:54:59.751
So the first one, when we increase it, the sympathetic works; and second one, when it decreases automatically, is the parasympathetic.

00:55:10.125 --> 00:55:13.042
Now, this parasympathetic is beyond our control.

00:55:20.000 --> 00:55:24.667
Now, due to these imbalances within ourselves, we develop so many problems.

00:55:31.167 --> 00:55:34.000
The first problem we have is of physical being.

00:55:38.501 --> 00:55:44.209
When there is imbalance within us, [a center gets] blocked.

00:55:50.959 --> 00:56:01.959
Now, how the cancer is caused is when… this is the center in the… in here, in the centre, then it's the left side and the right side sympathetic working.

00:56:10.999 --> 00:56:17.999
And who are in contact with the central nervous system, with the main brain.

00:56:23.834 --> 00:56:33.250
But when you start going too much to the right or to the left, these become smaller; [UNCLEAR] become smaller and smaller, till they break.

00:56:44.000 --> 00:56:49.417
As a result of that, you become on your own on your left side or on your right side.

00:56:56.083 --> 00:57:03.209
In the sense that your cells become arbitrary, start growing more than normal, so we call them malignant.

00:57:07.709 --> 00:57:08.999
YOGINI: Excuse me, Mother?

00:57:09.751 --> 00:57:11.125
SHRI MATAJI: What we call it — malignant.

00:57:12.459 --> 00:57:15.125
They… they start becoming bigger and bigger.

00:57:15.125 --> 00:57:19.709
When one cell starts overpowering other cells, they start becoming bigger and bigger.

00:57:20.083 --> 00:57:23.667
One part. Say, nose becomes bigger, eyes become bigger…

00:57:33.375 --> 00:57:35.501
And thus we say cancer is caused.

00:57:39.000 --> 00:57:43.751
There are so many physical troubles which are cause by imbalances.

00:57:49.209 --> 00:57:54.999
Even AIDS, AIDS and many other diseases are caused by this imbalance within us.

00:58:01.542 --> 00:58:02.959
Now, there is a solution.

00:58:06.250 --> 00:58:25.459
And the solution has been worked out now in Delhi University, people have… two doctors have passed PhD in their medical courses, which they call as [MD], with the subject as Sahaja Yoga.

00:58:35.959 --> 00:58:40.334
Now, they have worked on psychosomatic and as well as physical side.

00:58:47.042 --> 00:58:54.000
So, actually, what happens is that within ourselves lies the power to solve the problem.

00:59:02.792 --> 00:59:23.250
And when this power rises within us and passes through all the centres, opens this fontanelle bone area and becomes one with the all-pervading Power, the subtle Power, all of them get nourished and in balance.

00:59:43.083 --> 00:59:48.667
This power lies within all of us in the sacred bone called as sacrum.

00:59:56.667 --> 01:00:01.167
Now, the Greeks knew about it because they called it sacrum, means sacred.

01:00:07.751 --> 01:00:14.584
When this power rises, she passes through six centres within ourselves,

01:00:22.876 --> 01:00:26.542
who represent our physical, mental, emotional, spiritual beings.

01:00:32.876 --> 01:00:39.250
And she corrects, and she nourishes, and she balances all these centres.

01:00:45.626 --> 01:01:04.000
But that's not the only side — is the physical, or the emotional, or the spiritual, or the mental side — but the greater than that is that you become collectively conscious on your nervous system.

01:01:18.667 --> 01:01:20.626
That means you become empowered.

01:01:22.584 --> 01:01:31.709
You get the power to feel the centres of other people and your own centres.

01:01:38.667 --> 01:01:45.584
You can easily discern and find out what's wrong with other people and what's wrong with yourself.

01:01:51.292 --> 01:01:59.417
It may be physical, it may be emotional, it could be mental, or could be spiritual.

01:02:06.542 --> 01:02:11.417
I call it the blossom time, for modern times.

01:02:16.375 --> 01:02:20.626
As if you all are ready to achieve that stage,

01:02:27.083 --> 01:02:30.834
the state of Self-realization, of your second birth.

01:02:36.042 --> 01:02:43.999
This have been described in all the religions, in all the… big books, or prophets, or saints.

01:02:53.042 --> 01:02:55.417
After all, they would not be telling us lies.

01:02:59.709 --> 01:03:01.125
We have to be born again.

01:03:03.334 --> 01:03:09.834
But it's not like certifying yourself "I am born again" and doing all kinds of things which are absolutely destructive.

01:03:16.918 --> 01:03:24.751
But when this Kundalini rises — this power within you — you become absolutely a peaceful person within.

01:03:33.584 --> 01:03:40.250
I've known many people who form peace foundations, peace this, peace that — and they have no peace within.

01:03:49.125 --> 01:03:55.417
There are [UNCLEAR] [who won] Peace Nobel Prize, are such hot-tempered that you have to [UNCLEAR] [at] them with a barge pole.

01:03:56.250 --> 01:03:56.751
YOGINI: Excuse me?

01:03:56.751 --> 01:04:01.792
SHRI MATAJI: With a barge pole. You see, barge is a ship, a little ship, you see, you have to push it with a barge pole.

01:04:13.542 --> 01:04:17.918
You've got [UNCLEAR] at them, they are supposed to be Nobel Prize winners of peace.

01:04:25.918 --> 01:04:29.834
So all these artificial foundations are not going to help us.

01:04:35.083 --> 01:04:39.584
We have within ourselves this… innately placed, this power.

01:04:44.667 --> 01:04:50.334
And that power is… has been there all through your lives.

01:04:55.999 --> 01:05:00.042
You do not have to do anything about it.

01:05:03.667 --> 01:05:06.209
It is a spontaneous happening.

01:05:09.125 --> 01:05:11.125
Because it's a living process.

01:05:14.209 --> 01:05:17.459
It is a living process, like a seed can sprout.

01:05:22.125 --> 01:05:30.542
And once it sprouts… when you get your realization, you are amazed at your own capacities.

01:05:39.250 --> 01:05:42.125
You become dynamic but absolutely relaxed.

01:05:46.083 --> 01:05:47.459
There are no tensions.

01:05:50.375 --> 01:05:51.999
There are no pressures.

01:05:54.083 --> 01:05:58.626
And you are amazed at yourself how many things you are capable of.

01:06:04.417 --> 01:06:07.334
Then you realize that the knowledge you've had was so limited

01:06:12.959 --> 01:06:14.709
and was a relative knowledge.

01:06:17.209 --> 01:06:18.501
It was not absolute.

01:06:20.792 --> 01:06:31.292
So, actually, what happens that when you are born again, your spirit starts manifesting in your attention.

01:06:43.501 --> 01:06:48.250
In the light of the spirit you just see the real truth, the absolute truth.

01:06:54.876 --> 01:07:01.667
But this cannot be, this absolute truth cannot be forced on you in any way.

01:07:06.751 --> 01:07:13.792
This happening cannot take place if somebody tries to force you or tries to discipline you.

01:07:19.999 --> 01:07:21.876
Also you can't pay for it.

01:07:24.667 --> 01:07:28.584
Like the Mother Earth, Kundalini doesn't understand money.

01:07:34.501 --> 01:07:42.042
It's an actualization, is a genuine thing, and the innate thing within you.

01:07:50.083 --> 01:07:55.792
Even if you say, "Mother, give me my realization," I may not be able to do it.

01:07:56.083 --> 01:07:59.167
May be, may not be, there's no guarantee.

01:08:08.501 --> 01:08:16.542
You cannot become a member of a club of realized souls or cannot form a kind of an organization out of it.

01:08:24.626 --> 01:08:34.250
It is a happening within you, which you have to certify that you have felt the all-pervading Power on your fingertips.

01:08:43.959 --> 01:08:49.709
If you are honest and genuine in your seeking, I am sure you all should have it.

01:08:55.751 --> 01:08:58.918
As it is, we have two problems within us.

01:09:02.999 --> 01:09:04.417
Only two problems.

01:09:06.501 --> 01:09:10.125
One is that we have got certain conditionings.

01:09:15.584 --> 01:09:17.584
All kinds of conditionings we have got.

01:09:20.959 --> 01:09:26.834
Like, I can say I'm an Indian, and you are German, and you are English, and you are this, and you are that.

01:09:34.709 --> 01:09:40.667
Or I could say that I belong to this community, and that community, and that community.

01:09:46.125 --> 01:09:49.709
Or I may say I have read this book, and that book, and that book.

01:09:53.834 --> 01:09:55.918
All this is conditioning within us.

01:09:59.125 --> 01:10:01.209
You were born as a human being.

01:10:04.918 --> 01:10:11.250
And you have every right to get this union with the Divine, which we call as yoga.

01:10:20.209 --> 01:10:22.959
This is the real yoga.

01:10:26.417 --> 01:10:30.876
Because with that nourishment you just start getting transformed.

01:10:38.584 --> 01:10:40.459
You start seeing what's wrong with you.

01:10:44.999 --> 01:10:47.292
And you start seeing what's wrong with others.

01:10:50.834 --> 01:10:57.417
You develop a divine discretion by which you can see that this is wrong and this is right.

01:11:06.250 --> 01:11:15.459
It's not the mental analysis, but if you have realization, on your fingertips you can feel it what's the truth is.

01:11:24.250 --> 01:11:29.375
In these modern times, I would say your computer starts working.

01:11:35.417 --> 01:11:36.918
It's already programmed.

01:11:39.626 --> 01:11:40.751
It's all built-in.

01:11:43.125 --> 01:11:45.417
Only thing, it has to be connected to the mains.

01:11:47.459 --> 01:11:48.959
And then it starts working.

01:11:51.459 --> 01:11:56.250
And the programming is done with the absolute knowledge.

01:12:01.999 --> 01:12:03.667
So you make no mistakes.

01:12:08.501 --> 01:12:13.792
These are the minimum of minimum things that have to happen to human beings.

01:12:20.125 --> 01:12:27.999
If we have to save this world from further calamities, we have to get human beings transformed.

01:12:38.918 --> 01:12:49.459
We are so much worried of ecological imbalances — but not about human imbalances.

01:12:53.584 --> 01:12:59.626
And the second imbalance that we have is what we call as ego.

01:13:05.125 --> 01:13:11.167
That we think we have done this work, we have done that work… Is a feeling that we are very great.

01:13:19.918 --> 01:13:23.834
Now, for example, now we have very beautiful stage here.

01:13:24.334 --> 01:13:28.751
Out of the tree that falls dead, we have created another dead thing.

01:13:40.667 --> 01:13:43.999
Something from the dead do another dead.

01:13:48.626 --> 01:13:51.751
Have you ever done anything that is living?

01:13:56.918 --> 01:14:00.417
You can't even make an atom of your own.

01:14:04.459 --> 01:14:06.375
You cannot create anything.

01:14:08.792 --> 01:14:16.334
Whatever is created, you may try to change it, but you cannot create any element on your own.

01:14:25.999 --> 01:14:39.292
I'll tell you a joke, that sometimes some village people from India were asked to go by plane and were told not to carry too much luggage, because it won't be all right

01:14:50.792 --> 01:14:59.042
and the plane will feel the overloading, so it is better to take little things, few things with you.

01:15:06.459 --> 01:15:11.834
So these villagers sat in the plane and put all their luggage on their heads.

01:15:18.959 --> 01:15:20.626
They did it in their ignorance.

01:15:24.083 --> 01:15:26.542
So people asked them, "What are you doing?"

01:15:27.375 --> 01:15:30.417
They said, "We are trying to reduce the weight of the aeroplane."

01:15:37.999 --> 01:15:45.209
In the same way, we human beings feel that we are trying to reduce [the work] of the Creator.

01:15:53.501 --> 01:16:03.751
So this… this Mr. Ego from one side, and from the other side the conditioning creating superego; both of them meet and make a very hard nut here.

01:16:18.000 --> 01:16:22.626
And you become like a shell of a… of an egg, I should say.

01:16:27.250 --> 01:16:35.042
Now, in India, a realized soul is called as dvija, and… as well as the bird is called, called as dvija.

01:16:35.501 --> 01:16:37.417
Dvi-ja — means twice-born.

01:16:48.292 --> 01:16:55.584
Like the… like the bird is first born as an egg and then it becomes a bird.

01:17:03.459 --> 01:17:20.042
In the same way, a human being has to become a bird, in the sense he has to achieve his ultimate status, his ultimate destination.

01:17:29.667 --> 01:17:33.292
This is the epitome of evolution.

01:17:35.250 --> 01:17:44.999
At human level, we live relatively, but at this state we live in the absolute truth.

01:17:55.834 --> 01:18:04.999
When you achieve that state, then there is no question of understanding how we are related to each other.

01:18:13.334 --> 01:18:24.667
And the enjoyment that we get before realization looks like something artificial injections.

01:18:37.375 --> 01:18:44.792
Actually, in modern times, people are seeking joy, and when they don't get it, they want to have some sort of a sensation all the time.

01:18:54.792 --> 01:18:58.417
Whatever they are doing is in the search of joy.

01:19:03.167 --> 01:19:10.834
But the joy is within yourself, in your heart, resides as the embodiment of spirit.

01:19:19.584 --> 01:19:25.375
Joy is not double-faced like a coin, happiness and unhappiness. Joy is absolute.

01:19:33.334 --> 01:19:39.959
So one has to achieve that state, but for that you don't have to put in any efforts.

01:19:47.417 --> 01:19:52.667
It is like one candle which is enlightened can enlighten another candle very easily.

01:19:59.250 --> 01:20:04.459
In the same way, those who get realization can give realizations to others,

01:20:11.542 --> 01:20:18.375
transforming them into beautiful, wonderful universal human beings.

01:20:25.167 --> 01:20:32.959
There is complete freedom because no temptation can touch you.

01:20:39.292 --> 01:20:40.918
No one can deceive you.

01:20:45.709 --> 01:20:49.459
You understand each and every person inside out.

01:20:54.876 --> 01:21:01.667
In that state, you enjoy yourself and enjoy others who are like you.

01:21:08.667 --> 01:21:17.334
Unfortunately, in Germany, somehow, I don't know why, but Sahaja Yoga has not taken its roots.

01:21:27.250 --> 01:21:35.542
There are fifty another countries who have got people who have taken Sahaja Yoga very easily.

01:21:42.918 --> 01:21:52.542
They were all attacked by fake gurus, by… man-made religions — all kinds of things.

01:21:53.083 --> 01:21:58.125
But they could see with their pure intelligence that this is the truth.

01:22:10.250 --> 01:22:18.042
So I have to request you to have a look at it as a scientist.

01:22:18.999 --> 01:22:29.167
Keep your minds open, and if you receive your realization, then you will realize that what I'm saying is the absolute truth.

01:22:42.584 --> 01:22:43.876
May God bless you all!

01:23:04.083 --> 01:23:09.375
For about fifteen minutes, you can ask Me some questions.

01:23:16.334 --> 01:23:21.375
But I have not come here to take anything from you.

01:23:27.834 --> 01:23:33.167
I have just come here to give you what you have, your own, give.

01:23:39.834 --> 01:23:43.417
So there is no need to be offensive with Me for nothing at all.

01:23:49.292 --> 01:23:54.584
It's just what you have. I have come here to hand over your keys to you, for example.

01:24:01.459 --> 01:24:07.751
So, please ask Me questions, no doubt, but don't be unnecessarily aggressive.

01:24:15.334 --> 01:24:19.959
Because we should not waste the time so much on unnecessarily quarreling.

01:24:25.792 --> 01:24:28.250
Actually, I don't know how to quarrel, so it's a waste.

01:24:32.667 --> 01:24:36.626
All right. So, would we have your questions?

01:24:45.334 --> 01:24:46.000
Yes, please.

01:24:46.834 --> 01:24:50.709
SEEKER: Do You have any previous [UNCLEAR]?

01:25:10.459 --> 01:25:17.876
SHRI MATAJI: All right. We have, we have, in so many languages, and in America we have lots of people.

01:25:35.459 --> 01:25:39.626
(A seeker asks a question in German)

01:25:41.417 --> 01:25:44.751
YOGINI: He asked why do we need Your photograph to meditate.

01:25:45.459 --> 01:25:50.042
SHRI MATAJI: That you will know yourself. That My photograph has got vibrations.

01:25:50.792 --> 01:25:55.709
And when you start using the photograph, you get the vibrations from Me.

01:25:56.125 --> 01:26:00.918
Because in the beginning you have to depend on something to get to the vibrations.

01:26:01.209 --> 01:26:05.292
But if you have something else which can work it out, I have no objection.

01:26:06.167 --> 01:26:07.792
But I haven't seen anything like that.

01:26:30.751 --> 01:26:33.125
Is very big blessing, I should say.

01:26:36.083 --> 01:26:37.959
I should say, so it's a big blessing.

01:26:38.209 --> 01:26:46.083
Because now there are people who are meditating in [Sierra de] [UNCLEAR], if you must have heard the name of that African country.

01:26:46.459 --> 01:26:50.375
And they… I can't go there just now, so they can manage with My photograph.

01:26:50.375 --> 01:26:52.501
It's something a very big blessing, I should say.

01:27:03.209 --> 01:27:10.375
But in the beginning, you need not if don't want to. If you want, you can, it's your… your lookout.

01:27:20.334 --> 01:27:30.209
SEEKER: Speaking of Your photograph, do You believe that stones and woods, different types of [UNCLEAR] from the Earth…

01:27:32.751 --> 01:27:42.125
Do You believe that stones, crystals and woods, things that come from the Earth and such, do they have healing powers in them that we can use?

01:27:56.250 --> 01:28:01.751
SHRI MATAJI: All right. Now supposing I say I believe, or if I say I don't believe. You should not take Me for granted.

01:28:03.501 --> 01:28:05.667
You can find out from [your] Self-realization.

01:28:07.584 --> 01:28:12.292
I would not say anything I believe, because whatever I believe may not be the truth.

01:28:14.083 --> 01:28:17.083
So keep it open. So simple.

01:28:46.125 --> 01:28:49.834
It's only the politicians say, "I believe, I believe." Who are you?

01:28:56.959 --> 01:29:01.042
You see, I shouldn't say such a thing. I would like you to find out yourself.

01:29:07.334 --> 01:29:13.959
SEEKER: What are… what are the real benefits of Sahaja Yoga? But the real benefits, and not [UNCLEAR]?

01:29:14.334 --> 01:29:16.626
SHRI MATAJI: What I told you are unreal according to you?

01:29:17.417 --> 01:29:24.959
SEEKER: A real benefit [UNCLEAR] of Sahaja Yoga, but what I mean, what is the real benefit [UNCLEAR]?

01:29:26.083 --> 01:29:28.000
YOGINI: What is the benefits of Sahaja Yoga.
SHRI MATAJI: Eh?

01:29:28.000 --> 01:29:30.667
YOGINI: He is asking what is the benefit of Sahaja Yoga.

01:29:30.667 --> 01:29:32.999
SHRI MATAJI: All this I have told you. Are you an Indian?

01:29:34.042 --> 01:29:35.209
Do you understand Hindi?

01:29:36.459 --> 01:29:38.167
Should I tell you in Hindi language?

01:29:38.959 --> 01:29:43.375
(Speaks in Hindi)

01:29:47.083 --> 01:29:48.167
Have you understood now?

01:29:49.542 --> 01:29:57.834
(Repeats in English) When you tell the whole Ramayana, the question is asked who is… who… what was the relationship between Rama and Sita.

01:30:11.834 --> 01:30:15.125
YOGINI: Sorry, what…
SHRI MATAJI: What was the relationship between Rama and Sita.

01:30:19.334 --> 01:30:30.918
SEEKER: [UNCLEAR] all sane people who are doing at this time Hatha Yoga in Germany and the world and trying to find themselves… to reach the place…

01:30:30.999 --> 01:30:32.542
SHRI MATAJI: I can't hear you.
YOGI: Can you say it again?

01:30:33.999 --> 01:30:34.876
SEEKER: When you start going…

01:30:34.876 --> 01:30:36.584
SHRI MATAJI: You see, this is your heritage.

01:30:37.083 --> 01:30:40.250
You all Indians should know this is your heritage.

01:30:40.999 --> 01:30:43.375
And all the saints have described it.

01:30:44.000 --> 01:30:52.209
And now you are in the German country; you should understand that here it is you have to show them what we have in the [UNCLEAR].

01:30:52.209 --> 01:30:53.042
SEEKER: No, but we have… (continues in German)

01:30:55.209 --> 01:30:55.792
SHRI MATAJI: What he's saying?

01:31:12.334 --> 01:31:12.834
What's it?

01:31:21.292 --> 01:31:21.876
What's he said?

01:31:22.959 --> 01:31:25.334
Have you written there that My photograph should be used?

01:31:28.751 --> 01:31:29.876
You shouldn't have, I think.

