01:35:07.918 --> 01:35:18.292
Now, ha and tha means the right side and the left side, is the Surya Nadi and the Chandra Nadi, is the Sun and the Moon channels.

01:35:25.417 --> 01:35:34.999
And these were meant to give a balance to a personality by giving them precise asanas.

01:35:45.292 --> 01:35:47.209
But this balance for what?

01:35:53.250 --> 01:35:55.667
The balance was for the ascent.

01:36:00.334 --> 01:36:04.751
Like, when making aeroplane, we have to see its balance.

01:36:05.959 --> 01:36:11.334
In the same way, a human being was balanced, and the ascent was given.

01:36:24.834 --> 01:36:33.626
But in Sahaja Yoga, we have discovered a method by which, even there is no balance, you can ascent.

01:36:42.501 --> 01:36:43.999
Right is the speciality.

