01:39:07.834 --> 01:39:13.501
Now what is this centre, what is this centre, what is this centre — you have to understand it.

01:39:24.334 --> 01:39:36.083
But one thing has to be understood that if you are superficially seeking something and mentally trying to understand, this is beyond your mental ability.

01:39:45.999 --> 01:39:47.959
It doesn't work out for such people.

01:39:53.584 --> 01:39:55.667
All right. Let's have another.

01:39:56.334 --> 01:40:01.834
SEEKER: How old one has to be to get realization?

