01:40:39.250 --> 01:40:42.083
Let's see how far it works out.

01:40:53.292 --> 01:41:02.000
You have to do few things because I would like also you to know how to raise your own Kundalini.

01:41:11.918 --> 01:41:13.626
Which is a very simple thing.

01:41:16.459 --> 01:41:18.999
And which can be achieved without [UNCLEAR].

