01:41:52.834 --> 01:42:00.834
And it is not civil to disturb other people by your presence.

01:42:04.584 --> 01:42:11.999
Now, one humble request is that you have to take out your shoes, which is, I think, is not very difficult.

01:42:16.918 --> 01:42:18.876
And put your feet on the Mother Earth.

01:42:25.792 --> 01:42:31.626
Because that will give you help from the Mother Earth, who sucks in our problems.

01:42:38.876 --> 01:42:51.792
Better sit with parallel posture of both the legs, in this manner, because these are two different energies which are to be cleansed by the Mother Earth.

01:43:07.918 --> 01:43:14.209
Before you close your eyes, I have to make another humble request.

01:43:20.167 --> 01:43:24.667
Firstly, you have to know you are the temple of the Divine.

01:43:31.792 --> 01:43:36.792
And also that you are not to feel guilty about anything.

01:43:41.501 --> 01:43:46.292
I can feel from the chakras that you feel guilty for nothing at all.

01:43:52.292 --> 01:43:54.334
So, you should not feel guilty at all.

01:43:58.042 --> 01:44:01.709
On the contrary, you should be very pleasantly placed towards yourself.

01:44:08.334 --> 01:44:17.542
And understand that you are about to enter into the kingdom of your own glory and beauty.

01:44:28.375 --> 01:44:34.209
So please don't count your mistakes and don't blame yourself for anything.

01:44:42.334 --> 01:44:51.999
So with all confidence we'll have to close our eyes, but before that I'll tell you how to use your left hand and right hand.

01:45:03.250 --> 01:45:10.375
You have to put your left hand towards Me, expressing the desire to get your Self-realization.

01:45:11.292 --> 01:45:16.918
This way. You [can put it] on your lap or on your table, is better; if you have a table, it's good idea.

01:45:21.250 --> 01:45:22.501
Open like this.

01:45:27.334 --> 01:45:31.999
[UNCLEAR] should not be tense or anything, but should not be like that, should be like that.

01:45:37.375 --> 01:45:46.167
These are… are the ends of sympathetic nervous system and are represented in all of your centres within you, chakras.

01:45:54.999 --> 01:45:57.959
The another thing is, you'll use your right hand.

01:46:02.792 --> 01:46:05.501
Right hand has to be first put on your heart.

01:46:09.834 --> 01:46:12.292
Please all of you put your… on your heart, it's simple.

01:46:17.999 --> 01:46:21.125
Now, this is the place where resides the spirit.

01:46:28.501 --> 01:46:34.209
Then you have to put your right hand in the upper part of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

01:46:41.584 --> 01:46:44.334
We are working on the chakras on the left-hand side.

01:46:49.667 --> 01:46:52.459
Now, this is the centre of your mastery.

01:46:56.083 --> 01:46:59.959
Because if you are the spirit, also you become your own master.

01:47:07.417 --> 01:47:10.751
Now you put your right hand in the lower part of your abdomen.

01:47:15.959 --> 01:47:20.876
Now, this is the centre by which the divine laws work.

01:47:27.125 --> 01:47:32.751
So this is the centre which represents the pure knowledge.

01:47:38.250 --> 01:47:45.918
Now you'll go back again and put your hand on the left-hand side of your abdomen, in the upper part.

01:47:52.834 --> 01:47:56.042
Then you put your right hand on your heart again.

01:48:01.000 --> 01:48:07.501
Now you put your hand in the corner of your neck and your shoulder and put it to the right.

01:48:08.834 --> 01:48:09.501
[UNCLEAR]

