And put your head to the right.

01:48:17.542 --> 01:48:23.667
Now, this is the centre usually is catching today much more because this is the centre you catch when you feel guilty.

01:48:23.999 --> 01:48:25.542
Put your head to the right please.

01:48:33.292 --> 01:48:44.000
All right. Now, please take your hand on your forehead across like this and press it on both the sides.

01:48:44.167 --> 01:48:48.000
Press it on both the sides here. Press it on both the sides.

01:48:48.375 --> 01:48:53.167
Like that, on both the sides, with finger and this side, just press it like that.

01:49:00.250 --> 01:49:02.417
This is the centre of forgiveness.

01:49:06.292 --> 01:49:13.999
Now, you take back your hand and put it on the back side of your head, and put all the… whole of your head on your hand.

01:49:22.417 --> 01:49:24.834
Now, stretch your hand. Fully.

01:49:25.584 --> 01:49:37.918
Stretch your hand fully with the fingers backwards, and the centre of your palm you have to put it on your fontanelle bone, which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:49:49.209 --> 01:49:50.292
And press it hard.

01:49:51.334 --> 01:49:53.959
Move it seven times, your scalp.

01:49:58.167 --> 01:49:58.876
Clockwise.

01:50:01.999 --> 01:50:03.125
That's all you have to do.

01:50:11.584 --> 01:50:14.167
Now we will have to close the eyes.

01:50:14.626 --> 01:50:19.834
You can take your spectacles if it is disturbing you. Also helps your eyesight.

01:50:20.167 --> 01:50:26.626
Also, you can… if there's something tight on your body, you can loosen it.

01:50:27.042 --> 01:50:30.584
You have to be comfortable. You have to be comfortable…

01:50:43.918 --> 01:50:44.667
Now.

01:50:46.167 --> 01:50:48.459
Comfortable doesn't mean you should slump.

01:50:48.459 --> 01:50:53.334
But you should be straight, not pushing your head backwards or forwards but just straight.

01:51:01.667 --> 01:51:04.250
All right. Now close your eyes.

01:51:07.999 --> 01:51:10.125
This is how you take off, we can say.

01:51:14.042 --> 01:51:15.792
All right. Please close your eyes.

01:51:18.167 --> 01:51:21.959
I want you to be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

01:51:26.250 --> 01:51:29.751
Not to allow ill feeling towards yourself or anyone.

01:51:35.999 --> 01:51:40.125
Now please close your eyes, don't keep them open.

01:51:40.125 --> 01:51:42.834
Please close your eyes, all of you close you eyes.

