Now. Put your hand, right hand on the heart and left hand towards Me.

01:52:04.542 --> 01:52:17.709
Here you have to say, or ask a question which is very fundamental — you can call Me Shri Mataji or you can call Me Mother, whatever you like — "Mother, am I the spirit?"

01:52:17.709 --> 01:52:21.083
Ask this fundamental question three times. Please.

01:52:48.209 --> 01:52:55.000
This question takes you to an another question, because if you are the spirit you are also your master.

01:53:05.792 --> 01:53:12.959
So now take your hand down onto the upper part of your abdomen on the left-hand side and press it.

01:53:20.334 --> 01:53:26.876
Now, here you ask Me another fundamental question: "Mother, am I my own master?"

01:53:52.542 --> 01:53:53.709
Three times please.

01:53:59.999 --> 01:54:10.167
Now take your right hand in the lower part of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

01:54:21.000 --> 01:54:24.709
Here is the centre of pure knowledge.

01:54:24.999 --> 01:54:28.417
But I cannot force on you, so you have to ask for it.

01:54:28.751 --> 01:54:36.999
You have to say, "Mother, please, may I have the pure knowledge?"

01:54:40.667 --> 01:54:42.959
Or: "Mother, please give me the pure knowledge."

01:54:43.876 --> 01:54:49.167
All of you should put your left hand like this, not… some of you are just holding like that, that's not correct.

01:54:56.792 --> 01:54:59.792
Don't open your eyes, but she… somebody will come and correct you.

01:55:38.792 --> 01:55:42.417
Now… please don't open your eyes, please don't open your eyes.

01:55:45.042 --> 01:55:52.999
Ask this question, ask Me six times: "Mother, may I have the pure knowledge?" — because there are six petals.

01:56:07.584 --> 01:56:08.292
Now.

01:56:10.083 --> 01:56:13.334
When you say that, your Kundalini starts rising.

01:56:20.042 --> 01:56:40.125
To clear the way for the Kundalini, please try to put your right hand in the lower part of your ab— upper part of your abdomen on the left-hand side and press it, that centre of mastery.

01:57:00.876 --> 01:57:16.999
Here, with full confidence, you have to say, to open the centre you have to say, "Mother, I am my own master."

01:57:35.626 --> 01:57:40.542
Please say it with full confidence: "Mother, I am my own master."

01:57:48.501 --> 01:57:50.167
You have to say it ten times.

01:57:55.542 --> 01:57:57.083
Because there are ten petals.

01:58:10.250 --> 01:58:14.000
Now raise your right hand and put it on your heart.

01:58:21.042 --> 01:58:31.584
Here you have to say, again with full confidence, twelve times: "Mother, I am the spirit."

01:58:31.584 --> 01:58:33.250
This is the greatest truth.

01:59:04.250 --> 01:59:12.876
You have to know that the Divine is the ocean of love, grace and bliss.

01:59:14.292 --> 01:59:19.042
But above all, it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:59:33.042 --> 01:59:40.959
And whatever mistakes you must have committed — or you think you have committed — can be easily resolved by that ocean.

01:59:56.209 --> 02:00:06.792
So now raise your right hand in the corner of your neck and your shoulder and turn your head to your right side.

02:00:08.542 --> 02:00:13.709
From the… from the front side put the hand, not from the back side but from the front across.

02:00:23.042 --> 02:00:23.709
Here…

02:00:24.876 --> 02:00:29.125
Not from the back side please, put it from the front side.

02:00:35.334 --> 02:00:42.459
Here you have to say sixteen times with full confidence: "Mother, I am not guilty at all."

02:01:04.417 --> 02:01:07.751
"I am not guilty at all." Say it sixteen times.

02:01:13.459 --> 02:01:18.375
And if you feel even then guilty, then better punish yourself by saying hundred and eight times.

02:01:28.542 --> 02:01:31.167
You have to be pleasantly placed, as I have told you.

02:01:58.667 --> 02:02:06.209
Now please put your hand across over your forehead and press it on both the sides.

02:02:17.999 --> 02:02:26.417
At this point, you have to say, "Mother, I forgive everyone."

02:02:35.584 --> 02:02:40.542
Sometimes you feel it is very difficult to say.

02:02:47.542 --> 02:02:52.417
But whether you forgive or you don't forgive, it's a myth, you don't do anything.

02:03:00.542 --> 02:03:03.999
But if you do not forgive, you play into wrong hands.

02:03:10.292 --> 02:03:12.209
And you get emotionally disturbed.

02:03:15.792 --> 02:03:19.209
So say it from your heart, not how many times, say it from your heart.

02:03:28.375 --> 02:03:40.000
Now. Please take your hand back on the backside of your head and push it back, your head, on it.

02:03:49.876 --> 02:04:02.999
Just for your satisfaction — not to feel guilty, not to count your mistakes — you have to just say that "O Divine, if I have done any mistakes, please forgive me."

02:04:03.250 --> 02:04:05.292
But not to feel guilty at all.

02:04:31.209 --> 02:04:35.501
Now stretch your hand. Stretch your hand fully.

02:04:35.959 --> 02:04:44.709
Push back your fingers and put the centre of your palm on top of your head where there is a soft bone.

02:04:47.542 --> 02:04:50.167
Press it hard. Push back your fingers.

02:04:51.542 --> 02:04:53.000
Push back your fingers.

02:04:56.125 --> 02:04:59.375
Press it hard and move it seven times.

02:04:59.751 --> 02:05:10.834
At this time, you have to again ask for Self-realization because I cannot take your freedom.

02:05:12.459 --> 02:05:22.834
So you have to say it seven times: "Mother, please give me my realization," and move your hand with the pressure seven times.

02:05:22.834 --> 02:05:25.083
With the pressure. Move your scalp.

02:05:36.417 --> 02:05:38.542
Move it seven times with the pressure.

