And now see it, bend your head and see for yourself if there's a cool breeze.

02:08:27.501 --> 02:08:28.167
Bend your head.

02:08:39.250 --> 02:08:42.792
Now again, put your right hand again, once more.

02:08:43.959 --> 02:08:47.167
And see it for left hand. Bend your head again to see it.

02:08:53.542 --> 02:08:54.083
See higher.

