Mother, is this the Chaitanya?

02:09:29.000 --> 02:09:34.876
Is this the Power of Divine Love?"

02:09:39.584 --> 02:09:41.417
Ask this three times please.

02:09:49.876 --> 02:09:51.209
Now bring down your hands.

02:09:57.999 --> 02:10:12.709
